reviewText: Tim McGraw is a great singer in Country music! He has ruled the charts with the modern(progressive)Country sound that Garth Brooks first incorporated in his music, in 1989. Although I enjoy all the hits that McGraw has earned, I am disappointed with this DVD video collection. It is missing my favorite song/video: Everywhere....it's also missing Not A Moment Too Soon, Refried Dreams and Just To Hear You Say That You Love Me(with his beautiful wife, Faith Hill). I wish that Curb Records would have put out a more complete Tim McGraw video collection for his fans to thoroughly enjoy, like myself!
summary: Great Country singer....great songs, but missing more hits..
